<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3156444" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="16">$[officename] automatically suggests a cell range, provided that the spreadsheet contains data. If the cell range already contains a sum function, you can combine it with the new one to yield the total sum of the range. If the range contains filters, the Subtotal function is inserted instead of the Sum function.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3153189" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="3">Click the <emph>Accept</emph> icon (green check mark) to use the formula displayed in the input line.</paragraph>
